  "system": {
    "itemKey": "",
    "description": "<p>For the duration, you deal +1 Radiant damage on Martial Attacks.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Spell Enhancements</span></strong></span></p><p><strong>Damage: (2 MP, Repeatable)</strong> Your Attacks affected by this Spell deal +1 Radiant damage.</p><p><strong>Effortless: (1 MP)</strong> You no longer need to Sustain the Spell.</p><p><strong>Illuminating Strikes: (1 MP)</strong> Once per round, 1 target of an Attack affected by this Spell makes a Physical Save against your Save DC. <strong>Save Failure:</strong> The target sheds Dim Light in a 1 Space Aura and can’t benefit from 1/2 Cover or being Invisible.</p><p><strong>Guiding Strikes: (2 MP)</strong> Once per round, 1 target of an Attack affected by this Spell makes a Physical Save against your Save DC. <strong>Save Failure:</strong> Attacks made against the target add a d4 to the Check for 1 round.</p>",
